[05/06/2018 12:55:39] <font color="#00ffff">¡Tío Pinkie!</font>
[05/06/2018 12:55:41] <font color="#00ffff">Levántate.</font>
[05/06/2018 12:56:01] <font color="#0000ff">(Música)</font>
[05/06/2018 12:56:17] <font color="#00ff00">¡Bob Ford!</font>
[05/06/2018 12:56:20] <font color="#ffffff">(TOSE) Vete, Tommy.</font>
[05/06/2018 12:56:20] <font color="#00ffff">¡No!</font>
[05/06/2018 12:56:22] <font color="#00ff00">¡Sal de aquí!</font>
[05/06/2018 12:56:22] <font color="#00ffff">¡No quiero, no!</font>
[05/06/2018 12:56:26] <font color="#00ffff">¡Marta! ¡Se va a quemar ahí dentro!</font>
[05/06/2018 12:56:30] <font color="#00ffff">¡Está herida en el suelo,</font>
