[05/06/2018 19:53:20] <font color="#ffff00">¿Raviolis de caracol?</font>
[05/06/2018 19:53:21] <font color="#ffffff">Sí.</font>
[05/06/2018 19:53:21] <font color="#ffff00">Un beso.</font>
[05/06/2018 19:53:24] <font color="#ffff00">Traigo caracoles de Marie Therese.</font>
